name: KairosAgent
description: The anonymous review agent for Ethos Network. Kairos enables users to submit completely private reviews—positive, neutral, negative, or slash—without revealing their identity. 100% privacy preserving: no logs, no identity tracking, no stored information about reviewers. Only users with reputable Ethos profiles can submit anonymous reviews, ensuring accountability while protecting privacy. Search any X account or ENS to review. Reviews include a "from reputable account" qualifier so recipients know feedback comes from credible sources.
